msgstr "Añade una columna Proveedor a la tabla de la lista de productos de WooCommerce."

#: front-end/vendors/class-brikpanel-vendor-settings.php:113
msgid "Stock orders (purchase orders)"
msgstr "Pedidos de stock (órdenes de compra)"

#: front-end/vendors/class-brikpanel-vendor-settings.php:116
msgid "Place orders to vendors, track expected vs. received dates, and let BrikPanel calculate average lead time per supplier."
msgstr "Realiza pedidos a proveedores, registra fechas previstas vs recibidas y deja que BrikPanel calcule el tiempo medio de entrega por proveedor."

